# Convert2MP3

Convert2MP3 is a simple tool to convert audio files to MP3 format.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

    git clone <https://github.com/yourusername/convert2mp3.git>
    cd convert2mp3

2. Create a virtual environment:

    python3 -m venv venv

3. Activate the virtual environment:

    On macOS and Linux:

    source venv/bin/activate

    On Windows:

    .\venv\Scripts\activate

4. Install the dependencies:

    pip install -r requirements.txt

